:0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:54:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝巴打你肯同我吹又幫下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即刻睇睇先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n希望你搵到方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n希望啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nStep out your comfort zone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0fe8162163148b3a12c38ba9d8769d5b19b4f71","tid":59500,"uid":12158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:59:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 頂住，讀埋個HD先啦！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我會頂住 應該頂到。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好諗咁多無謂嘢搞到自己唔開心。見步行步，做好手頭上嘅工作先。如果你每一件小事都做得好，最後整體都會成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}